{"tid":1511232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"整標語，舉牌，要求盡快通過民主及人權法案，必要時制裁香港","createTime":"2019-08-27T12:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T03:17:22.000Z","uid":210140,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"023521559d92447243fb397b76a8a0bc5e815e1c","tid":1511232,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"之後既遊行除左美帝旗，仲應該整標語呼籲美國盡法通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508994/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508994/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n有兩件垃圾建制議走左去誤導美帝議員<br />\n雖然泛民四子解釋左佢地只係呼籲制裁官員<br />\n但呢種減辣力度係唔夠架<br />\n除左制裁官員外，必要時制裁香港<br />\n我地無得再輸，呢張係最後一張皇牌<br />\n而家已經開始吹風想推行緊急法，又開始大搜捕<br />\n黎緊既遊行，如果有美帝旗既就舉美帝旗<br />\n無既，可以做到既就印唔同既標語表示我地香港人主流意願<br />\n就係通過法案！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOBKoUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOBKoUE.jpg&h=150472be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家如果覺得唔夠好，亦可以參與設計，兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n<br />\nP.S.關於買旗既問題，除左門店大地旗Ｘ外，網店維城士Ｘ亦有售美帝旗"},{"pid":"d0fd584aceefcbd01e01b603216ed9baedcca591","tid":1511232,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=891d1937\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=e01d4c9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=htt